{
  "texts": [
    "Until now, no standardized operational models have been produced for RPA activities.",
    "Mr. Kristina Romero and his technical team from M/s.",
    "InfoCap Networks LLC (InfoCap), based in San Diego, present a proposed demonstration of RPA processes [17], as seen in Fig 1.",
    "According to Flechsig,Anslinger,and Lasch [18], this technology approach has the potential to revolutionize entrepreneurship operations by automating manual tasks.",
    "This shift would reduce reliance on human labor, decrease time consumption, and address the issue of error-prone content in business processes."
  ]
}